item.title: Goldie - Deviation Presents 'Metalheadz History Session', XOYO, London - 27.06.15 by Metalheadz
item.description:
Goldie - Deviation Presents 'Metalheadz History Session', XOYO, London - 27.06.15 by Metalheadz

For the 3rd and final set of the night we had Goldie taking it back to the 90's in front of a sold out crowd, this is the last of the 3 recordings that we are uploading from this memorable mid-summer event.
